originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    c.kind AS company_type,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT k.keyword, ', ') AS keywords,
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.info) AS num_personal_infos
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_type c ON mc.company_type_id = c.id
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
LEFT JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
LEFT JOIN 
    person_info p ON a.person_id = p.person_id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000
    AND c.kind LIKE '%Production%'
GROUP BY 
    a.name, t.title, c.kind
ORDER BY 
    actor_name, movie_title

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."ACTOR_NAME", "t5"."ACTOR_NAME") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t5"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t5"."COMPANY_TYPE", "t5"."KEYWORDS", "t5"."NUM_PERSONAL_INFOS"
FROM (SELECT "t2"."name", "t2"."title", "t2"."kind", MIN("t2"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("t2"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", MIN("t2"."kind") AS "COMPANY_TYPE", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS", COUNT(DISTINCT "person_info"."info") AS "NUM_PERSONAL_INFOS"
FROM (SELECT "s1"."id", "s1"."person_id", "s1"."name", "s1"."imdb_index", "s1"."name_pcode_cf", "s1"."name_pcode_nf", "s1"."surname_pcode", "s1"."md5sum", "cast_info"."id" AS "id0", "cast_info"."person_id" AS "person_id0", "cast_info"."movie_id", "cast_info"."person_role_id", "cast_info"."note", "cast_info"."nr_order", "cast_info"."role_id", "t0"."id" AS "id1", "t0"."title", "t0"."imdb_index" AS "imdb_index0", "t0"."kind_id", "t0"."production_year", "t0"."imdb_id", "t0"."phonetic_code", "t0"."episode_of_id", "t0"."season_nr", "t0"."episode_nr", "t0"."series_years", "t0"."md5sum" AS "md5sum0", "movie_companies"."id" AS "id2", "movie_companies"."movie_id" AS "movie_id0", "movie_companies"."company_id", "movie_companies"."company_type_id", "movie_companies"."note" AS "note0", "t1"."id" AS "id3", "t1"."kind", "movie_keyword"."id" AS "id4", "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "movie_id1", "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
FROM "movie_keyword"
RIGHT JOIN ("cast_info" INNER JOIN ("movie_companies" INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000) AS "t0" ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "t0"."id" INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "company_type"
WHERE "kind" LIKE '%Production%') AS "t1" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "t1"."id") ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "t0"."id" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id") ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "t0"."id") AS "t2"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "t2"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
LEFT JOIN "person_info" ON "t2"."person_id" = "person_info"."person_id"
GROUP BY "t2"."name", "t2"."title", "t2"."kind"
ORDER BY 4, 5) AS "t5"
